opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 19th day of September, 2005, the “Application of Philadelphia Housing Authority for Reconsideration and Modification of this Court’s Dismissal of the Petition for Allowance of Appeal” is hereby DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
